]
(if: $sawBilly is false)[
☐ Speak with Billy Costa on the gyptian ship
]


[[Return to the start->Start]]
]


:: Ship Deck {"position":"1500,150","size":"100,100"}


Lyra climbs to the deck. Cold wind whips her face. Stars blaze above the canals, and far on the horizon, a faint green shimmer.

Pan swoops overhead as a seagull.

(if: (count: (history:), "Ship Deck") >= 3)[

Pan drops onto the railing, hard. *"Lyra! Look!"*

A shadow descends from the sky — a woman riding a branch of cloud pine as though it were a flying horse. A **witch**.

(set: $foundWitch to true)

[[Speak with the witch->Witch Encounter]]

](else:)[

The night is quiet. Lyra has the strange sensation of being watched from above, but when she looks, there's only stars.

*"Did you feel that, Pan?"*

*"Yes. We should come up here again. I think something's waiting for us."*

[[Return to the ship->The Gyptian Ship]]
]


:: Speak with Ma Costa {"position":"1500,50","size":"100,100"}


(if: (count: (history:), "Speak with Ma Costa") >= 2)[
Ma Costa pours another cup of chocolate and looks at Lyra with eyes full of love and grief.

*"There's something you need to know, child. Something about your mother."*

Pan goes absolutely still.

*"Your mother is Mrs Coulter."*

The silence that follows is deafening. Lyra feels the floor tilt beneath her. Pan cycles through forms in a frantic blur — cat, bird, mouse, snake —

*"And my father?"* Lyra manages.

*"Lord Asriel."*

(set: $knowsMotherTruth to true)
(set: $panState to "shattered")

[[Return to the ship->The Gyptian Ship]]

](else:)[
Ma Costa wraps her in a blanket and presses a mug of hot chocolate into her hands.

*"You're a brave one, Lyra. The gyptians have always watched over you, even if you didn't know it."*

*"Why?"* asks Lyra.

Ma Costa hesitates. *"Come back and see me again. There are things you need to hear, but first you need to trust me."*

(set: $allies to $allies + 1)

[[Return to the ship->The Gyptian Ship]]
]


:: Start {"position":"100,200","size":"100,100"}

(set: $accuracy to 0)
(set: $allies to 0)
(set: $coulterRoute to false)
