]
]

[[Head for the main doors with all the children->Escape With Everyone]]
[[Crawl through the vents with Roger only->Escape With Roger]]


:: The Gyptian Ship {"position":"1400,200","size":"100,100"}



The gyptian ship smells of timber and warm stew. Lyra feels safer than she has in weeks. Around her, families prepare for the expedition North to rescue their children.

Pan curls in ermine form on her lap. *"What now?"*

The gyptians are nearly ready to sail, but there's time to prepare.

[[Speak with Ma Costa->Speak with Ma Costa]]
[[Go up to the deck->Ship Deck]]
[[Find Billy Costa->Billy Costa]]
[[Listen to rumours on the wharf->Wharf Rumours]]
[[Consult the alethiometer->Consult Alethiometer Ship]]

(if: (count: (history:), "The Gyptian Ship") >= 3)[

---

John Faa, king of the gyptians, rises to his feet. *"It's time. We sail North."*

[[Set sail for Bolvangar->Departure North]]
]


:: The Machine {"position":"3000,200","size":"100,100"}



(set: $timer to 30)

## The Intercision Machine

Roger is inside the cage. Salcilia screams in the other compartment. The machine hums to life. A silver blade — made of something that isn't metal — descends slowly.

Pan shrieks: *"LYRA, DO SOMETHING!!"*



(live: 1s)[
(set: $timer to it - 1)
(if: $timer <= 8)[⏱ $timer SECONDS](else:)[⏱ $timer seconds]
(if: $timer is 0)[
(stop:)(goto: "Too Late")
]
]

[[Destroy the machine with your bare hands->Destroy Machine]]
[[Scream for the gyptians->Call for Help]]
[[Create a distraction so Roger can escape->Create Distraction]]


:: Too Late {"position":"3200,400","size":"100,100"}

(set: $panState to "broken")

Lyra couldn't decide in time.

The machine completed its cycle. When the hum fades, Roger is still alive, but something in his eyes has gone out. Salcilia is gone. A tuft of white fur lies on the floor of the cage.

*"Where's Salcilia?"* Roger asks, his voice hollow. *"I'm cold."*

Pan sinks against Lyra's chest, weeping the way only a dæmon can: soundless, a tremor that reaches the bone.

Lyra has failed. But the other children are still here.

[[Get Roger and the others out->The Escape]]


:: Try to Escape {"position":"250,300","size":"100,100"}

(set: $panState to "nervous")

Lyra eases the wardrobe door open, but the hinge betrays her with a sharp creak. An elderly scholar — Professor Dorian — catches her mid-step.

*"Lyra? What on earth are you doing here?"*

Pan shifts into a cat, trying to look innocent. Lyra improvises — something about chasing her cat through the corridors. It's a weak lie, and they both know it.

The Professor studies her, severe but oddly gentle. *"Go to bed. And Lyra — be careful what you overhear in this college. Not everything that's hidden is wicked."*

She missed Asriel's full presentation, but the Professor's warning stays with her. The next morning, she finds a note slipped under her door: *"Dust is not what the Magisterium claims. Library, north section, third shelf."*

And alongside the note: a golden instrument wrapped in cloth, with a message from the Rector. *"This is an alethiometer. Guard it well, Lyra. It tells the truth."*

(set: $allies to $allies + 1)

[[Head to the rooftops->Jordan Rooftops]]


:: Ventilation Infiltration {"position":"2150,100","size":"100,100"}


(set: $dice to (random: 1, 6))

Lyra pulls herself into the shaft. Tight, dark, freezing. Pan goes ahead as a mouse, scouting the way.

(if: $dice >= 3)[
The shaft opens into an empty storeroom. Lyra drops silently onto a stack of cardboard boxes. Pan shakes off the dust.

*"We're in,"* he whispers.

[[Explore the corridors->Bolvangar Doors]]

](else:)[
The shaft narrows. Pan squeaks: *"We don't fit, Lyra!"*

She has to reverse, losing precious time. A guard hears the scraping and comes to investigate.

*"Run!"* Pan hisses.

(set: $allies to $allies - 1)
(if: $allies < 0)[(set: $allies to 0)]

[[Evade the guard->Chase Scene]]
]


:: Visit Roger {"position":"550,200","size":"100,100"}

Down in the kitchens, Roger is peeling potatoes alongside the other kitchen boys. His dæmon Salcilia plays as a terrier at his feet, tumbling with Pan.

*"Lyra!"* Roger grins. *"Come to steal buns again?"*

*"Roger — have you heard of the Gobblers?"* Lyra drops her voice.

His face darkens. *"My mate Billy, the gyptian boy — disappeared last week. His mum's beside herself. They say it was them."*

Lyra takes his hand. *"Whatever happens, I'll look after you. I promise."*

A promise that will weigh more than she can possibly know.

[[Back to the rooftops->Jordan Rooftops]]


:: Wharf Rumours {"position":"1500,350","size":"100,100"}


(set: $rumour to (either: "They say Lord Asriel is imprisoned in Svalbard, guarded by the armoured bears", "Magisterium airships have been spotted flying north, loaded with scientific equipment", "A witch was shot down over the sea — they say she carried a message for the gyptians"))

Lyra wanders the wharf where gyptians load provisions. Conversations drift in low voices.

An old gyptian leans close: *"$rumour"*

(if: $rumour contains "Asriel")[
Pan thinks aloud: *"Your father, a prisoner. Maybe the alethiometer can show us how to free him."*
](else-if: $rumour contains "airships")[
Pan scans the sky: *"The Magisterium is preparing something big up north. We need to be careful."*
](else:)[
Pan whispers: *"The witches are on our side. That's something, isn't it?"*
]

[[Return to the ship->The Gyptian Ship]]


:: Witch Encounter {"position":"1650,100","size":"100,100"}

The witch alights with the softness of a falling leaf. Her dæmon, a grey goose, settles beside her. She looks young, but her eyes hold centuries.

*"I am Serafina Pekkala, queen of the Lake Enara witch clan,"* she says. *"I've been watching you, Lyra. The alethiometer speaks to you, doesn't it?"*

Lyra nods, unsure what to say.

*"The witches know a prophecy about a girl who can read the alethiometer without being taught. A girl who will decide the fate of Dust. That girl is you."*

Pan trembles. Lyra swallows hard.

*"When you reach Bolvangar, remember this: Dust is not sin. Dust is what makes us human."*

Serafina rises into the night and vanishes among the stars.

(set: $allies to $allies + 2)

[[Return to the ship->The Gyptian Ship]]


:: Wrong Reading 1 {"position":"700,400","size":"100,100"}

The needles spin aimlessly, rejecting her interpretation. Lyra frowns.

Pan sighs. *"That's not it. But don't worry — you'll get the hang of it."*

Frustrating. But Lyra Belacqua has never been the kind to give up.

[[Back to the rooftops->Jordan Rooftops]]


:: Wrong Reading 2 {"position":"1650,500","size":"100,100"}

The needles spin wildly, rejecting the interpretation. Lyra sighs.

*"It's all right,"* Pan says. *"What matters is we know where we're going. The alethiometer will guide us when it counts."*

[[Return to the ship->The Gyptian Ship]]


:: StoryStylesheet [stylesheet]

/* ============================================
   THE GIRL AND THE DUST — UI THEME
   Dark atmospheric / Northern Lights / Gold
   ============================================ */

@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;600;700&family=Crimson+Text:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&display=swap');

/* --- CSS VARIABLES --- */
:root {
  --bg-deep: #060a14;
  --bg-dark: #0a1025;
  --bg-card: rgba(12, 18, 42, 0.85);
  --gold: #c9a84c;
  --gold-light: #f0d77b;
  --gold-dim: #8a7233;
  --aurora-green: rgba(45, 212, 160, 0.12);
  --aurora-purple: rgba(124, 92, 191, 0.10);
  --aurora-blue: rgba(56, 140, 224, 0.08);
  --text-main: #ddd3c1;
  --text-dim: #9e9585;
  --text-bright: #f5eed9;
  --danger: #c44;
  --danger-glow: rgba(204, 68, 68, 0.3);
  --success-green: #4ecca3;
  --font-display: 'Cinzel', serif;
  --font-body: 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
  --transition-speed: 0.6s;
}

/* --- GLOBAL RESET & BASE --- */
tw-story {
  background: var(--bg-deep);
  color: var(--text-main);
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: 1.15em;
  line-height: 1.8;
  min-height: 100vh;
  overflow-x: hidden;
  position: relative;
}

tw-sidebar {
  display: none !important;
}

/* --- NORTHERN LIGHTS BACKGROUND EFFECT --- */
tw-story::before {
  content: '';
  position: fixed;
  top: -50%;
  left: -20%;
  right: -20%;
  height: 100%;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 10%, var(--aurora-green) 0%, transparent 50%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 5%, var(--aurora-purple) 0%, transparent 45%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 15%, var(--aurora-blue) 0%, transparent 55%);
  animation: auroraPulse 12s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 0;
}

tw-story::after {
  content: '';
  position: fixed;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
  background-image:
    radial-gradient(1px 1px at 10% 20%, rgba(255,255,255,0.4) 0%, transparent 100%),
    radial-gradient(1px 1px at 30% 65%, rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 0%, transparent 100%),
    radial-gradient(1px 1px at 55% 15%, rgba(255,255,255,0.5) 0%, transparent 100%),
    radial-gradient(1px 1px at 70% 45%, rgba(255,255,255,0.2) 0%, transparent 100%),
    radial-gradient(1px 1px at 85% 80%, rgba(255,255,255,0.35) 0%, transparent 100%),
    radial-gradient(1px 1px at 15% 85%, rgba(255,255,255,0.25) 0%, transparent 100%),
    radial-gradient(1.5px 1.5px at 45% 50%, rgba(201,168,76,0.4) 0%, transparent 100%),
    radial-gradient(1px 1px at 90% 10%, rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 0%, transparent 100%),
    radial-gradient(1px 1px at 5% 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0.2) 0%, transparent 100%),
    radial-gradient(1px 1px at 60% 90%, rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 0%, transparent 100%),
    radial-gradient(1px 1px at 25% 35%, rgba(255,255,255,0.15) 0%, transparent 100%),
    radial-gradient(1.5px 1.5px at 78% 62%, rgba(201,168,76,0.3) 0%, transparent 100%);
  animation: starsTwinkle 6s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 0;
}

@keyframes auroraPulse {
  0% { opacity: 0.4; transform: translateX(-3%) translateY(0); }
  33% { opacity: 0.7; transform: translateX(2%) translateY(-2%); }
  66% { opacity: 0.5; transform: translateX(-1%) translateY(1%); }
  100% { opacity: 0.6; transform: translateX(3%) translateY(-1%); }
}

@keyframes starsTwinkle {
  0% { opacity: 0.5; }
  50% { opacity: 0.8; }
  100% { opacity: 0.6; }
}

/* --- PASSAGE CONTAINER --- */
tw-passage {
  max-width: 680px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 2.5em 2em;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  animation: passageFadeIn var(--transition-speed) cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94) both;
}

@keyframes passageFadeIn {
  0% {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(18px);
    filter: blur(2px);
  }
  100% {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
    filter: blur(0);
  }
}

/* --- TYPOGRAPHY --- */
h1 {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--gold);
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 2.2em;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(201,168,76,0.3), 0 0 60px rgba(201,168,76,0.1);
  margin-bottom: 0.3em;
}

h2 {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--gold);
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 1.5em;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
}

em {
  color: var(--text-bright);
  font-style: italic;
}

strong {
  color: var(--gold-light);
  font-weight: 600;
}

hr {
  border: none;
  height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0%, var(--gold-dim) 50%, transparent 100%);
  margin: 2em 0;
  opacity: 0.5;
}

/* --- STYLIZED CHOICE BUTTONS --- */
tw-link, .enchantment-link {
  display: block;
  color: var(--gold);
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 0.85em;
  font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  text-decoration: none;
  padding: 14px 22px;
  margin: 10px 0;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201,168,76,0.08) 0%, rgba(201,168,76,0.03) 100%);
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
  border-radius: 4px;
  transition: all 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  cursor: pointer;
}

tw-link::before, .enchantment-link::before {
  content: '›';
  position: absolute;
  left: 10px;
  top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%) translateX(-5px);
  opacity: 0;
  color: var(--gold-light);
  font-size: 1.3em;
  transition: all 0.35s ease;
}

tw-link:hover, .enchantment-link:hover {
  color: var(--gold-light);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201,168,76,0.15) 0%, rgba(201,168,76,0.06) 100%);
  border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.5);
  padding-left: 32px;
  box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(201,168,76,0.1), inset 0 0 20px rgba(201,168,76,0.03);
  text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
}

tw-link:hover::before, .enchantment-link:hover::before {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: translateY(-50%) translateX(0);
}

tw-link:active, .enchantment-link:active {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201,168,76,0.22) 0%, rgba(201,168,76,0.1) 100%);
  transform: scale(0.98);
}

/* --- INLINE LINKS (for non-choice links) --- */
tw-expression[name="link"] tw-link {
  display: inline;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0;
  background: none;
  border: none;
  border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--gold-dim);
  border-radius: 0;
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: 1em;
  letter-spacing: normal;
}

tw-expression[name="link"] tw-link:hover {
  padding-left: 0;
  box-shadow: none;
  border-bottom-color: var(--gold);
  background: none;
}

tw-expression[name="link"] tw-link::before {
  display: none;
}

/* --- IMAGES --- */
img {
  display: block;
  margin: 1.5em auto;
  max-width: 100%;
  border-radius: 6px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.4), 0 0 40px rgba(201,168,76,0.05);
}

/* --- TIMER BAR --- */
.timer-container {
  width: 100%;
  height: 6px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  border-radius: 3px;
  margin: 1.2em 0;
  overflow: hidden;
  position: relative;
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.1);
}

.timer-bar-fill {
  height: 100%;
  border-radius: 3px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold) 0%, var(--gold-light) 100%);
  box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(201,168,76,0.5);
  transform-origin: left;
}

.timer-bar-fill.t30 {
  animation: timerShrink30 30s linear forwards;
}
.timer-bar-fill.t20 {
  animation: timerShrink20 20s linear forwards;
}

@keyframes timerShrink30 {
  0% { width: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--success-green), var(--gold-light)); }
  50% { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), var(--gold-light)); }
  80% { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--danger), var(--gold)); }
  100% { width: 0%; background: var(--danger); box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--danger-glow); }
}

@keyframes timerShrink20 {
  0% { width: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--success-green), var(--gold-light)); }
  50% { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), var(--gold-light)); }
  80% { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--danger), var(--gold)); }
  100% { width: 0%; background: var(--danger); box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--danger-glow); }
}

.timer-text {
  text-align: center;
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 0.85em;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  color: var(--gold);
  margin-top: 0.5em;
  text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
}

.timer-text.urgent {
  color: var(--danger);
  text-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--danger-glow);
  animation: urgentPulse 0.5s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}

@keyframes urgentPulse {
  from { opacity: 0.7; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}

/* --- PAN'S STATE INDICATOR --- */
.pan-state {
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 0.7em;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold-dim);
  background: rgba(201,168,76,0.06);
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.12);
  padding: 4px 14px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 1em;
}

/* --- ENDING CARDS --- */
.ending-card {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201,168,76,0.08) 0%, rgba(12,18,42,0.9) 100%);
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 1.5em 2em;
  margin-top: 2em;
  text-align: center;
}

.ending-card .ending-title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  color: var(--gold);
  font-size: 0.8em;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 0.5em;
}

.ending-card .ending-note {
  font-size: 0.9em;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  font-style: italic;
}

/* --- SECRET ENDING GLOW --- */
.secret-glow {
  text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(201,168,76,0.5), 0 0 40px rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
  animation: secretPulse 3s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}

@keyframes secretPulse {
  from { text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(201,168,76,0.3), 0 0 40px rgba(201,168,76,0.1); }
  to { text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(201,168,76,0.6), 0 0 60px rgba(201,168,76,0.2); }
}

/* --- REQUIREMENT CHECKLIST --- */
.checklist {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  border-radius: 6px;
  padding: 1em 1.5em;
  margin: 1em 0;
  border-left: 3px solid var(--gold-dim);
}

.checklist-item {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 0.8em;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  padding: 0.3em 0;
  color: var(--text-dim);
}
